  "instructions": [
    "Wash and dry the romaine lettuce, then chop into bite‑sized pieces.",
    "Slice the cucumber into half‑moon shapes and halve the cherry tomatoes.",
    "Peel and finely slice the small red onion; set aside.",
    "Steam the mushrooms for 4 minutes until just tender, then chill.",
    "In a small bowl whisk together lemon juice, Greek yogurt, minced garlic, and olive oil until smooth.",
    "Sprinkle the ground poppy seeds into the dressing and whisk again to combine.",
    "In a large salad bowl combine lettuce, cucumber, tomatoes, onion, steamed mushrooms, olives, and crumbled feta.",
    "Pour the dressing over the salad and toss gently to coat all ingredients.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning with salt and pepper if desired.",
    "Serve immediately for a fresh, crisp, and indulgent Greek salad."
